==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Not seeing (somebody) for a day is like being apart for three autumns.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī rì bù jiàn, rú gé sān qiū

===Phrase===
'''[[一]][[日]][[不]][[见]]，[[如]][[隔]][[三]][[秋]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') A single day apart seems like three years.

===Alternate forms===
[[一]][[日]][[不]][[見]]，[[如]][[隔]][[三]][[秋]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

